{
  "text": "Human MSCs were purchased from Lonza, cultured and characterized, as previously described [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] . hMSCs were maintained in the presence of cysteine free Mesenchymal Stem Cells Basal Medium (MSCBM, Lonza, Basel, Switzerland). All cell preparations at different passages of culture expressed the typical MSC markers, CD105, CD73, CD44, CD90, and CD146 and not hematopoietic markers like CD45, CD14 and CD34, as evaluated by flow cytometry assay [CITATION_4] (see Table S1 for the complete list of antibodies used in this study).",
